reviews.text: Nice bar close to main street. Nearby there are a lot of similar bars with beers, drinks and some of them with shisha. Food was quite good - rather european cuisine than thai national food. Good place for a evening drinks with friends.

Maze bar is near the end of a strip where a lot of bars are. You can always find plenty of people here as the weekend approaches. You can get a good variety of beers and bar chow here. The theme is somewhat Aztec for me but it's really a mix with even Greek letters in the decor. A lot of expats hang around here s well as sophisticated locals
Its good to sit outside and enjoy the night. Food was great and the concept of the restaurant is nice especially their glassware :)
a bar with a theme, from decor to glasses. around $500 per head for 4 bottles of wine.
Nice concept bar with good happy hour prices.
